{"type": "article", "id": 9999, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-26T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8577, "name": "蓝牙键盘"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 10631, "name": "咖啡滤杯"}, {"id": 10632, "name": "UNDERCOVER"}, {"id": 10633, "name": "EKOCYCLE"}, {"id": 8635, "name": "Coca Cola"}, {"id": 10634, "name": "OTM"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 7332, "name": "KFC"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235358doVSi2ePfm05c19z.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tHamburger Lamp by UNDERCOVER \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tUNDERCOVER 最近在十几年后重新推出了其经典的“汉堡灯”，这款灯发布于 2002 年，曾以其圆圆的眼睛和可爱的牙齿赢得了人们的喜爱。我们预计一旦发售很快会被抢空，所以建议感兴趣的提前关注起来。这款灯预计售价 148 美元，将于 6 月底发布，<a href=\"http://www.medicomtoy.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123829Y3vcshCrfKXOI5d0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123829a9kRgSPYiDETlXw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34828496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021238301sXg9YryfLEozAb7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34217507\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tNato by EKOCYCLE \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t可口可乐与 will.i.am 合作打造的时尚生活时尚品牌 EKOCYCLE 在继和 MCM 合作推出包袋，和 Adidas，Beats，LEVI’S 等品牌合作后，最近又和 Misfit 合作推出了特别版的 Nato 腕带。EKOCYCLE 一向推崇环保生活态度，这次也不例外，这些腕带的材料全部来自可口可乐瓶子中的可再生聚酯塑料，在环保的基础上保证时尚度和舒适度。目前单款腕带售价 49.99 美元，三款装则为 99.99 美元，<a href=\"http://store.misfit.com/products\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123830ETsi5NVbakMCodWf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021238342ekVHMoYy3a9Uh0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5525\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123835nJQqhKxML285yAzp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021238354zkIWdt6euqUrmA8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123836s592S0UOyucEFCwY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123836t2hXsbYM9c1QCUFd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123837VLAhcOq6WXeK39Rf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123837xUjszZSNF2hdXya3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tSunglass by Retrosuperfuture x Andy Warhol \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">意大利眼镜品牌 Retrosuperfuture 联合 </span>Andy Warhol 推出了四款新的太阳镜，分别命名为BabyBaby、Nicolou、VelvetDarling 和 Ultracandy，这些都是常常出入 Andy Warhol 工作室的朋友的名字，而在造型上，有红色心形，猫眼镜框配黑色镜片等个性十足的设计。产品将会在 6 月份登陆线上和线下门店，<a href=\"http://retrosuperfuture.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123838ncgTbBQOMuFkKRw4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123838My2jq8ch7ZzlYFvD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123839vJTZYDuQrNHs9Ifc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123839XqHL6NiApdGxRC3J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tPhree by OTM \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t以色列科技公司 OTM 推出了一款叫做 “Phree” 的手写笔，采用 3D 激光专利技术，跟踪使用者的手部动作和精确的笔画，可以在任何表面上书写，如手机，平板电脑，笔记本电脑，电视等，并且即时在手机上显示出来。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"http://otmtech.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123840cwhU0zvWpkYbTrMZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123840b3FDnCweqRHoYcXh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123841YGz0JERgSKZwyj43.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123841pH6FqRXDQJhxAnUI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123842jpJeUMvQux1yzDgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13569682\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021238423R4XdFbV8gs7lpIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123843hoKsRp6zxFikQBgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tDripper Set by Visvim \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t时尚品牌 Visvim 旗下的 Little Cloud Coffee 咖啡馆最近推出了一款叫做 “Dripper Set” 的滴漏式咖啡滤杯，包括印有民族风花纹的陶瓷杯子和金属支架，看上去十分复古。产品将于品牌指定门店发售。这是<a href=\"http://visvim.tv/dissertations/little_cloud_coffee.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Little Cloud Coffee 官方主页</a>，点击可以查看更多信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123843Sct1KXVLIa8AndOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021238435C6QT1ND32IftanF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tTray Typer by KFC\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t肯德基为了解决吃炸鸡的时候手上沾满油污而无法打字的问题，推出了这一款叫做 “Tray Typer” 的键盘。这是一个可充电的超薄蓝牙键盘，会随着肯德基的盘子连同食物一起端给你，通过蓝牙与附近的智能手机连接在一起，就可以愉快地一边吃炸鸡薯条，一边和朋友聊天了。实在是“孤独者的通行证”呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123844q5nLOoWGpAQfuCDR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55378973\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123844aKmrJfhqosIdceiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123845ZVsKrlgtjuziAFqv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n"}